Class FolActionName

java.lang.Object
org.tweetyproject.logics.commons.syntax.TypedStructureAdapter
org.tweetyproject.logics.commons.syntax.Predicate
org.tweetyproject.action.signature.FolActionName
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<TypedStructureAdapter>, TypedStructure
public class FolActionName extends Predicate
This class represents an action name. It is implemented as a fol predicate to allow for easy grounding of action descriptions.
Author:
Sebastian Homann
